{
  "category": "Foundation — Fork Identity",
  "description": "**Milestone:** Foundation — Fork Identity\n\nRename the binary from 'opencode' to 'ava' (packages/opencode/bin/opencode -> bin/ava). Update src/global.ts to use 'ava' for XDG config dir (~/.config/ava/), data dir (~/.local/share/ava/), and database name (ava.db). Update CLI entry in src/index.ts: scriptName('ava'), all yargs command descriptions. Update package.json name to 'protocli' and bin field.\n\n**Files to Modify:**\n- packages/opencode/bin/opencode\n- packages/opencode/src/global.ts\n- packages/opencode/src/index.ts\n- packages/opencode/package.json\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] Running ./bin/ava starts the TUI\n- [ ] Config is read from ~/.config/ava/\n- [ ] Data is stored in ~/.local/share/ava/ava.db\n- [ ] CLI help shows 'ava' not 'opencode'\n\n**Complexity:** small\n\n**Guardrails:** If this phase involves new or changed behavior, include tests that verify correctness. If this phase adds, removes, or changes a user-facing feature, API endpoint, configuration option, or service, update the relevant documentation in `docs/` to reflect those changes.",
